short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Stick Duel a action packed online fighting game. Try to win each medieval themed battle as you go to war against your opponents.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Stick Duel Battle online game is available in the chrome web store just install it and play Stick Duel Battle online game.


Controls:-

Player 1 Controls
Arrow keys = move
O = throw
L = shoot

Player 2 Controls
WASD = move
R = throw
F = shoot

Additional Games:- Racing, Arcade, Shooting, Girls, Dressing, Adventure, etc
